data.description:
Price reduction!  Motivated sellers!  

Introducing this charming brick home nestled in a quiet neighborhood close to the college, schools and shopping.  3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this property offers comfort and convenience. The spacious backyard is nicely maintained and features a storage shed, chain-link fence, and a majestic pecan tree providing shade for the yard. 

Each bedroom comes equipped with walk-in closets and ceiling fans, ensuring ample storage and comfort. Relax in the living room or dine in the cozy dining area. The kitchen is efficiently laid out with a breakfast bar for casual meals.

Convenient laundry facilities are located in the garage. This home is perfect for first-time homebuyers or those looking to downsize. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your new home sweet home!
